      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="8862nd">8862nd meeting</inline>, on <docDate date="2021-09-17" refersTo="#adoptionDate">17 September 2021</docDate></docTitle>
